A long time ago there was a woman lived at hill .She worked in a merchant's house .She had to walk down the hill every day to collect water from the stream .She had two pots to carry water , which she hung upon a pole and carried over her shoulder .
 After some time one of the pot had a crack ,she still used it .The woman would fill to the bring and walk back of the hill .By the time she reached house the cracked pot would only be half - full . When the cracked pot saw water filled to the top in the other pot , it began to feel desolate. 
  After a few year the cracked pot spoke to the lady ," I apologize for my flaws .I spill half of the water . I am of no good !"
The lady replied ,"As we return to the master's house , I want you to look the path we walk ."
 The next time the pot carefully observed the path . On his side of the pot noticed beautiful flowers growing in abundance , while the other side was still dry . The lady said ," I had always known about your cracks  and I took advantage of it to water those beautiful flower along the way."

"Every one of us is unique and we have our own flaws .The
 perfect ones are always flawed .I find beauty in your flaws ."The lady said .

Instead of searching mistakes in others we should focus on the bright side of its character . Life will be more happy and inspired .
